# Clinical Workflows and Care Pathways

## Overview

ZARISH SPHERE provides standardized clinical workflows optimized for humanitarian and low-resource settings. These workflows are designed to deliver quality care while managing resource constraints, ensuring patient safety, and maintaining data integrity.

