### Emergency Conditions Requiring Immediate Care

#### Life-Threatening Conditions

- **Airway Obstruction** - Complete or partial airway compromise
- **Severe Respiratory Distress** - RR greater than 30, SpO2 less than 90%
- **Cardiac Arrest** - No pulse, apnea
- **Severe Hemorrhage** - Active bleeding, hypovolemic shock
- **Major Trauma** - Multiple injuries, GCS less than 8
- **Severe Burns** - greater than 20% TBSA or airway involvement
- **Anaphylaxis** - Severe allergic reaction
- **Diabetic Ketoacidosis** - DKA with altered mental status

#### Urgent Conditions

- **Chest Pain** - Possible cardiac origin
- **Stroke Symptoms** - FAST positive
- **Severe Abdominal Pain** - Possible surgical abdomen
- **Fever greater than 39°C** - With systemic symptoms
- **Dehydration** - Moderate to severe
- **Fractures** - Open or displaced

## Care Pathways

### Acute Respiratory Infections (ARI) Pathway

#### Initial Assessment

```json
{
  "pathway": "ARI",
  "step": "initial_assessment",
  "criteria": {
    "symptoms": ["cough", "fever", "difficulty_breathing"],
    "duration": "<14 days",
    "severity": "mild_to_moderate"
  },
  "exclusions": [
    "chronic_respiratory_disease",
    "immunocompromised",
    "age_<2_months"
  ]
}
```

#### Decision Tree

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[ARI Presentation] --> B{Respiratory Distress?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Severe ARI]
    B -->|No| D{Fever >38.5°C?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Moderate ARI]
    D -->|No| F[Mild ARI]
    
    C --> G[Urgent Referral]
    E --> H[Antibiotic Consideration]
    F --> I[Supportive Care]
    
    H --> J{Pneumonia Signs?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Amoxicillin 500mg TID]
    J -->|No| L[Supportive Care]
    
    I --> M[Paracetamol PRN]
    I --> N[Fluids + Rest]
    K --> O[Follow-up 48hrs]
    L --> P[Follow-up 3 days]
```

