#### Treatment Algorithm

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[BP >140/90] --> B{Stage 2 or >160/100?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Start 2-drug therapy]
    B -->|No| D{Stage 1 or comorbidities?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Single agent + lifestyle]
    D -->|No| F[Lifestyle modification 3-6 months]
    
    C --> G[ACEi/ARB + CCB or Thiazide]
    E --> H[ACEi/ARB or CCB or Thiazide]
    F --> I{BP controlled?}
    I -->|No| H
    I -->|Yes| J[Continue lifestyle]
    
    G --> K[Follow-up 1 month]
    H --> K
    K --> L{BP at goal?}
    L -->|Yes| M[Maintenance therapy]
    L -->|No| N[Add third agent or increase dose]
```

