## Clinical Decision Support

### Diagnostic Algorithms

#### Fever Assessment Algorithm

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Fever ≥38°C] --> B{Age <2 months?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Urgent Referral]
    B -->|No| D{General Danger Signs?}
    D -->|Yes| C
    D -->|No| E{Stiff neck or bulging fontanelle?}
    E -->|Yes| F[Meningitis - Urgent Referral]
    E -->|No| G{Malaria risk area?}
    G -->|Yes| H[RDT + Treatment]
    G -->|No| I{Respiratory symptoms?}
    I -->|Yes| J[ARI pathway]
    I -->|No| K{Diarrhea present?}
    K -->|Yes| L[Diarrhea pathway]
    K -->|No| M[Other causes - investigate]
```

